                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">WhatsApp 最新推出了 iOS 平台上的更新，WhatsApp 版本 24.14.81 增长了动态影片和音讯的长度至 60 秒，新添了设定上传相片和影片画质的功能，并更新了 WhatsApp 的通话介面。</p><figure id="attachment_1250843" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250843" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250843 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1757-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1757-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1757.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250843" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲WhatsApp 24.14.81 版本记录</span></figcaption></figure><h2>动态</h2><figure id="attachment_1250844" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250844" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250844 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1759-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1759-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1759.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250844" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲动态影片和音讯的长度至 60 秒</span></figcaption></figure><h2>可设定相片/影片的上传画质</h2><figure id="attachment_1250845" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250845" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250845 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1760-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1760-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1760.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250845" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲在设定中进入「储存空间及数据」</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1250846" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250846" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250846 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1761-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1761-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1761.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250846" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲可设定媒体上载画质</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1250847" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250847" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250847 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1762-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1762-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1762.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250847" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲有普通的标准画质和高清画质选择</span></figcaption></figure><h2>新通话介面</h2><figure id="attachment_1250852" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250852" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250852 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsapp_new_interfa-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsapp_new_interfa-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsapp_new_interfa.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250852" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲旧版本 WhatsApp 通话介面为上拉式</span></figcaption></figure><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://indianexpress.com/article/technology/social/whatsapp-starts-rolling-out-new-interface-for-voice-video-calls-on-ios-7416623/">The Indian Express</a></p><figure id="attachment_1250841" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250841" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250841 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1755-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1755-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1755.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250841" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲新通话介面变成五按钮设计</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1250842" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1250842" style="width: 268px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1250842 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1756-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1756-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1756.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1250842" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲最左的选项按钮</span></figcaption></figure><p>更新后的通话介面取消了以往的上拉式选单而转成五按钮设计，以选项按钮取代了上拉式选单。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/11/samsung-galaxy-ai-4/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy AI 或将扩展至第三方应用程式     WhatsApp 或有实时翻译功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/create-ai-powered-images-within-whatsapp-chats/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 将加入 Meta AI   用户可人工智能生成图像</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/29/wfsfaa-scam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">被冒认发出虚假 WhatsApp 讯息　职学处澄清并呼吁市民提防</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/17/whatsapp-update-24-14-81/software/iphone-app/">WhatsApp 更新 iOS 介面　动态影片长度达 60 秒 + 预设相片上传画质</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
